{"tid":674352,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"話香港無可能獨立嗰啲人根本就邏輯有問題","createTime":"2018-05-22T15:09:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T03:49:29.000Z","uid":22675,"like":32,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a7e3b78a0d9d38b402e2b3384b5f5f22d6bda098","tid":674352,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T15:09:28.000Z","msg":"香港好有可能獨立，但未必係大家想像嗰種，有可能係大量蝗蟲完全入侵香港，同化曬消滅曬所有香港人，跟住班蝗蟲就正式變曬做&quot;香港人&quot;，只不過係完全唔識廣東話咁解，根住中共再不斷再引入蝗蟲，舊蝗蟲忍受唔到班新蝗蟲於是搞革命爭取獨立，中共見班蝗蟲都係自己人，於是畀蝗蟲玩新加坡式獨立，最後香港真正成功獨立，不過嗰種獨立係一個香港人都無咁解，就好似等於菠蘿包無菠蘿，埃及無古埃及人，同埋一樣行獨裁制，我好懷疑中共終極目標就係想要一個咁嘅香港"},{"pid":"1e4abe1e50943ff20ea29cc45e7350727c1177cd","tid":674352,"uid":28366,"like":15,"dislike":10,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T15:12:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/21/175529_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F21%2F175529_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ff67997c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/21/175532_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F21%2F175532_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=906f363c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/21/175535_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F21%2F175535_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=659acf98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/21/175537_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F21%2F175537_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=6ec4e89b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/21/175539_d0b32446