{"pid":"54113cf0558d742dfc72cc1077c85997fba66a67","tid":674352,"uid":34927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24becc2bf24bd4916524b5066b244b4619d373d4","tid":674352,"uid":125976,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e215d48c942f87ac20433e4a5171ab781083f3d1","tid":674352,"uid":163350,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d7660273a165d4ada55137c809fc92e29561d8d7","tid":674352,"uid":104699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T16:55:11.000Z","msg":"又屈移民就自私，宜家個形勢係香港必亡，你一點火種都唔留就真係自私。<br />\n<br />\n無興中會同盟會，無海外華人課金，點推翻都滿清。你係要個個精英綁兩個炸彈衝去d689777度先唔自私啊？你幾時先衝到埋xi總度啊？<br />\n<br />\n保存實力都要反，你地咪靠自己獨囉，睇下你地點獨法"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T16:58:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T17:02:12.000Z","msg":"所以早講咗，香港人乃支族同源，雖曾受大英貴族指教，但本質未改，都係成事不足、敗事有餘嘅東亞病夫。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T17:39:51.000Z","msg":"諗起個張咩中國人每天被勞役卻有統智者的智慧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個世界我諗無咩人種會屌自己人想攬住一齊死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你就係呢種"},{"pid":"82cb4447afde27c90e09a59e0b0507c0561311a7","tid":674352,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54113cf0558d742dfc72cc1077c85997fba66a67","tid":674352,"uid":34927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24becc2bf24bd4916524b5066b244b4619d373d4","tid":674352,"uid":125976,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e215d48c942f87ac20433e4a5171ab781083f3d1","tid":674352,"uid":163350,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T16:58:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T17:02:12.000Z","msg":"所以早講咗，香港人乃支族同源，雖曾受大英貴族指教，但本質未改，都係成事不足、敗事有餘嘅東亞病夫。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T17:39:51.000Z","msg":"諗起個張咩中國人每天被勞役卻有統智者的智慧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個世界我諗無咩人種會屌自己人想攬住一齊死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" c